      "value": {
        "latex": "$\\sum_{(i,j)\\in(\\N^*)^2}\\frac1{(i+j)^\\alpha}$.",
        "html": "<p><span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(\\sum_{(i,j)\\in(\\N^*)^2}\\frac1{(i+j)^\\alpha}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "ce802959-beee-4809-9aaf-7d7bcf5bbc15",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Regroupement à $i+j$ constant $ \\Rightarrow $ CV ssi $\\alpha > 2$.",
        "html": "<p>Regroupement à <span class=\"math inline\">\\(i+j\\)</span> constant\n<span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\Rightarrow\\)</span> CV ssi <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(\\alpha &gt; 2\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "5835dc68-c6ff-4f29-bac9-861085d92e59",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$\\sum_{(i,j)\\in(\\N^*)^2}\\frac1{\\strut i^\\alpha +j^\\alpha}$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\sum_{(i,j)\\in(\\N^*)^2}\\frac1{\\strut\ni^\\alpha +j^\\alpha}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "6ee7ee6f-bd05-46ad-9ed4-a457614430ea",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Pour $\\alpha\\ge 1$ on a par convexité~:\n             $2^{1-\\alpha}(i+j)^\\alpha \\le i^\\alpha+j^\\alpha \\le (i+j)^\\alpha$\n             donc il y a convergence ssi $\\alpha > 2$.",
        "html": "<p>Pour <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\alpha\\ge 1\\)</span> on a par\nconvexité : <span class=\"math inline\">\\(2^{1-\\alpha}(i+j)^\\alpha \\le\ni^\\alpha+j^\\alpha \\le (i+j)^\\alpha\\)</span> donc il y a convergence ssi\n<span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\alpha &gt; 2\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
